Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:42.68,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.2\bord0\fnImpact\shad0\fs90\b1\c&HFCFFFC&\move(340,218,420,218)}MF Ghost
